inputFiles.beam.dat:
RNDSEED      	89736501     ! Random seed
JPART0       	2            ! Incident particle type
TMAX0      	58.0  1.5       ! Incident energy; (MeV/nucl)
NSTAT       3000    0       ! NSTAT, Step of saving
STRAGG          2            ! Straggling: 0-Off 1-Gauss, 2-Vavilov
MSCAT           2            ! Mult. scatt 0-Off 1-Gauss, 2-Moliere
NUCRE           1            ! Nucl.Reac. switcher: 1-ON, 0-OFF
BEAMPOS 0 0 -51 ! Position of the beam
BEAMDIR 0.0 0.0 ! Direction of the beam
inputFiles.detect.dat:
Geometry Cyl
    Name CylZ_Mesh
    R 0 5 1
    Z -50 0 400

Geometry Mesh
    Name YZ_Mesh
    X -0.25 0.25 1
    Y -2 2 80
    Z -50 0 400

Geometry Cyl
    Name BeforePMMA
    R 0 5 1
    Z -45.05 -44.95 1

Geometry Cyl
    Name Isocenter
    R 0 5 1
    Z 2.95 3.05 1

Filter
    Name Protons
    Z == 1
    A == 1
Filter
    Name Primaries
    Z == 1
    A == 1
    GEN == 0
Filter
    Name Secondary_protons
    Z == 1
    A == 1
    GEN >= 1
Output
    Filename z_profile.bdo
    Geo CylZ_Mesh
    Quantity Dose 
    Quantity Fluence Protons
    Quantity Fluence Primaries
    Quantity AvgEnergy Primaries

Output
    Filename yz_profile.bdo
    Geo YZ_Mesh
    Quantity Dose 
    Quantity Fluence Protons
    Quantity Fluence Primaries

Output
    Filename before_pmma.bdo
    Geo BeforePMMA
    Quantity Dose 
    Quantity AvgEnergy Primaries
    Quantity AvgEnergy Protons
    Quantity AvgEnergy Secondary_protons
    Quantity Fluence Protons
    Diff1 0 70 700 
    Diff1Type E

Output
    Filename isocenter.bdo
    Geo Isocenter
    Quantity Dose 
    Quantity AvgEnergy Primaries
    Quantity AvgEnergy Protons
    Quantity AvgEnergy Secondary_protons
    Quantity Fluence Protons
    Diff1 0 70 700 
    Diff1Type E
inputFiles.mat.dat:
